io.github.prolobjectlink.db.prolog

Interface PrologProgrammer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Platform
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractProgrammer

    public interface PrologProgrammer
extends Platform
    Prolog Programmer is a mechanism responsible of generate a Prolog code from Java classes include in Java runtime jars. Every class found in Java runtime jars produce one equivalent prolog file that link your Java class.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jose Zalacain

      • codingInclusion

        @Deprecated
void codingInclusion(PrintWriter out,
                                  String jarEntryName)
        Deprecated. Use codingInclusion(PrintWriter, String, String) instead.
        Set the file inclusion directive used by Prolog implementation for include Prolog file harness (e.g obj/prolobject.pl). The path in the inclusion directive consider the folder levels from generated file to Prolog harness.
        Parameters:
        out - writer to print generation messages
        jarEntryName - String that represent the full qualified jar entry name inside jar file
        Since:
        1.0
